cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new Graph Neural Network that combines recent advancements in the field, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The theoretical contributions and comparisons with existing models also suggest a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence.
